text.tspan: Share of males vs. females with autistic spectrum disorder,
Share of males versus females with autistic spectrum disorder, which is inclusive of autism and Asperger Syndrome.
This prevalence is age-standardized to compare between countries and with time.
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease
